title: KnockSpy v1.11
description:
KnockSpy v1.11

KnockSpy is an application for monitoring and data logging many engine parameters, including the ignition timing and knock control systems, in the 1990-93 Nissan 300zx over the CONSULT diagnostics port.  KnockSpy features data logging, graphing, realtime map-tracing, gauge display, and Active Tests - allowing control over many engine sub-systems for diagnostics purposes.
